e\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"la World Boxing - une confrontation\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"enjeux sont \\u00e9troitement li\\u00e9s\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"sport power \\u00bb de la Russie\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e9l\\u00e9ment\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"de Vladimir Poutine\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le 1erao\\u00fbt 2024, en quart de finale de la comp\\u00e9tition f\\u00e9minine de boxe en cat\\u00e9gorie moins de 66 kilos des Jeux olympiques de Paris, Angela Carini abandonne d\\u00e8s le premier round apr\\u00e8s quarante-six secondes de combat contre l'Alg\\u00e9rienne Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103664941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421630116, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quart de finale de la comp\\u00e9tition\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"f\\u00e9minine de boxe\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"de Paris\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"L'Italienned\\u00e9clare\\u00e0La Gazzetta dello Sport: \\u00ab Au deuxi\\u00e8me coup, je ne pouvais plus respirer ; ce n'est pas une d\\u00e9faite pour moi.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"L'Italienned\\u00e9clare\\u00e0La Gazzetta dello Sport\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"Au deuxi\\u00e8me coup\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"je ne pouvais\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"respirer\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"ce n'est pas une d\\u00e9faite pour moi\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00bb Elle ne serre pas la main de son adversaire apr\\u00e8s l'annonce de la d\\u00e9cision, mais pr\\u00e9cise peu apr\\u00e8s que ce n'\\u00e9tait pas intentionnel et s'en excuse.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"serre pas\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"main de son\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"mais\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angela Carini ne semble pas avoir \\u00e9mis un quelconque jugement discriminatoire remettant en cause la f\\u00e9minit\\u00e9 de la boxeuse alg\\u00e9rienne.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"la\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"alg\\u00e9rienne\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pourtant, ses d\\u00e9clarations et son comportement vont \\u00eatre d\\u00e9form\\u00e9s et utilis\\u00e9s jusqu'\\u00e0 d\\u00e9clencher une pol\\u00e9mique mondiale, r\\u00e9v\\u00e9lant une claire ligne de partage : d'un c\\u00f4t\\u00e9, les pro-Imane Khelif, qui sont aussi pour la plupart des d\\u00e9fenseurs de la cause LGBT et des droits des minorit\\u00e9s ; de l'autre, les promoteurs d'une morale ultra-conservatrice port\\u00e9e par la droite radicale, qui estiment qu'elle n'aurait pas d\\u00fb \\u00eatre autoris\\u00e9e \\u00e0 concourir.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 0.9999989655394422, \"rank\": 1.0280354878968362e-06, \"text\": \"LGBT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"et son comportement vont \\u00eatre d\\u00e9form\\u00e9s\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"d'un c\\u00f4t\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"les pro-Imane Khelif\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"la\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"la\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"cause\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"de l'autre\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"les\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"d'une morale ultra-conservatrice port\\u00e9e par\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"la droite radicale\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"qui estiment qu'elle n'aurait pas d\\u00fb \\u00eatre autoris\\u00e9e \\u00e0 concourir\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"La premi\\u00e8re ministre italienne, Giorgia Meloni, a ainsiestim\\u00e9que le combat \\u00ab n'\\u00e9tait pas sur un pied d'\\u00e9galit\\u00e9 \\u00bb.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giorgia Meloni\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giorgia_Meloni\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"La premi\\u00e8re ministre italienne\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"a ainsiestim\\u00e9que le combat \\u00ab n'\\u00e9tait pas sur un pied d'\\u00e9galit\\u00e9 \\u00bb\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vladimir Poutine, Donald Trump, Elon Musk, mais aussi J. K. Rowling et des milliers d'utilisateurs des r\\u00e9seaux sociaux n'ont pas \\u00e9t\\u00e9 en reste dans leurs d\\u00e9clarations blessantes, au point qu'Imane Khelif a d\\u00e9cid\\u00e9 deporter plainte pour \\u00ab harc\\u00e8lement et haine en ligne \\u00bb.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poutine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Poutine\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poutine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poutine\"}, {\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999994179234, \"rank\": 5.818918000183573e-10, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"score\": 0.9986187884794978, \"rank\": 0.0013808428896454291, \"text\": \"K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\"}, {\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"des r\\u00e9seaux sociaux\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"n'ont pas \\u00e9t\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"d\\u00e9clarations blessantes\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"au point qu'Imane Khelif\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"a d\\u00e9cid\\u00e9 deporter plainte pour\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"en\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"ligne \\u00bb\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les m\\u00e9dias du monde entier ont donn\\u00e9 un \\u00e9cho consid\\u00e9rable \\u00e0 cette pol\\u00e9mique, qui restera comme l'un des \\u00e9pisodes marquants de JO de Paris\\u2026 et qui r\\u00e9v\\u00e8le des enjeux n'ayant pas grand chose \\u00e0 voir avec le taux de testos\\u00e9rone d'Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2446, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journal_officiel_de_la_R\\u00e9publique_fran\\u00e7aise\", \"score\": 0.990594616690264, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JO\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journal_officiel_de_la_R\\u00e9publique_fran\\u00e7aise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journal_officiel_de_la_R\\u00e9publique_fran\\u00e7aise\"}, {\"begin\": 2452, \"end\": 2457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2740191742465766e-210, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2523, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doeg_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"taux\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doeg_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doeg_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Les m\\u00e9dias\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"entier ont\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"donn\\u00e9 un \\u00e9cho consid\\u00e9rable \\u00e0 cette pol\\u00e9mique\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"qui restera comme l'un\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"et qui r\\u00e9v\\u00e8le des enjeux n'ayant pas grand\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"D\\u00e8s la fin du combat contre Carini, la pol\\u00e9mique enfle rapidement, les d\\u00e9tracteurs de Khelif ne manquant pas de rappeler que, un peu plus d'un an plus t\\u00f4t, en mars 2023, lors des championnats du monde tenus en Inde, l'Alg\\u00e9rienne avait \\u00e9t\\u00e9 disqualifi\\u00e9e par l'Association internationale de boxe (IBA), de m\\u00eame que la Taiwanaise Lin Yu-Ting (qui deviendra le 11 ao\\u00fbt championne olympique des moins de 57 kilos \\u00e0 Paris), \\u00e0 l'issue d'un contr\\u00f4le de f\\u00e9minit\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 3013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Inde\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inde\"}, {\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"l'Association\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9899883637575383, \"rank\": 0.005503638359442814, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2897, \"ti